title: Tumi Sinclair Camila Tote
description:
In this video we take a closer look at the Tumi Sinclair Camila Tote.  For more details or to place an order please visit us at Abt.com: http://www.abt.com/resources/pages/search.php?keywords=tumi%20sinclair%20camila&utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=TUMISINCLAIRCAMILA_20170517

Features:
- Primary Material: Textured Coated Canvas 
- Fits up to 15"
- Interior Features:
1 zip pocket on front wall
Front envelope pocket with magnetic snap closure
1 open pocket
1 velvet-lined jewelry pocket
Padded laptop compartment
1 pen loop
Key leash
- Exterior Features:
Single zip entry to main compartment
Padded removable/adjustable shoulder strap
Back compartment with magnetic snap closure
Hidden cellphone pocket
Leather top handle
Gusseted front pocket for volume expansion
Footed bottom for added protection and stability
- Height: 11"
- Width: 17.5"
- Depth: 4.75"
